{"tid":1936624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣確診男高中生傳染兩位同學　但父母沒有受到感染","createTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T13:42:10.000Z","uid":209657,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cf73ae0d3455e1a8cee02e88685f7b3e3ea28f85","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/16/2458801-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F16%2F2458801-XXL.jpg&h=1c8327fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今(21日) 中央流行疫情指揮中心記者會中提到，案59例傳染給同班兩位同學，分別為案103例跟案130例，彼此之間因為教室座位非常接近所以受到感染，但是案59例的父母並未受到感染，一般外界認為家人的接觸時間更長，且生活在同一個空間，理論上傳染的機會更大，然而案59例卻是傳同學沒傳家人，最主要的原因在於學生間的互動更親密。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc27cdeea6686a400c33f6a405eb548221e86136","tid":1936624,"uid":334025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4a5ab74be84dd44b528adf0e289f0f72b4db52","tid":1936624,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d02a79f7254c40185f7071985c27506b749034","tid":1936624,"uid":11301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"學生間的互動更親密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9a71fe864b2b0555b145e96c257a8411db61d","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/16/2458800-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F16%2F2458800-XXL.jpg&h=87266b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心指揮官陳時中表示：並不是說接觸到病毒就會一定會感染，有的會，有的不會；中央流行疫情指揮中心疫情監測組組長周志浩更補充說明，案59例傳同學卻沒傳給父母，即便以常理，跟父母的接觸機會會比較多，實際上學生之間的接觸與互動會比父母更親密，因此可以解釋為何肺炎傳染給同學但父母沒有受感染。"},{"pid":"bbe88bdf854fee8cd5e362310ec4e1fbd47725cf","tid":1936624,"uid":12404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"男仔同男同學扑嘢好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f4d756116020ae09b68c2b985aaec8dec78ad8","tid":1936624,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbe88bdf854fee8cd5e362310ec4e1fbd47725cf","tid":1936624,"uid":12404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"男仔同男同學扑嘢好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"咪係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蕉流蕉流"},{"pid":"4125e55ab1fc9de1bc9e0e6a4613a6a3b64ff3b2","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:34:30.000Z","msg":"指揮中心是在15日公布第59例確診，<span style=\"color: red;\">該名男高中生1月與家人同遊希臘，3月5日返台</span>，但12日才出現喉嚨痛症狀，13日因咳嗽、流鼻水及頭痛就醫，是開學後首例學生確診停課，當時匡列接觸者66人，有57人需居家隔離，包括36名同班同學、7名老師還有家人及友人。<br />\n<br />\n家人外遊都無事。。"},{"pid":"3548c22d9d35d259e4a267732e6acd82a4cddf55","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbe88bdf854fee8cd5e362310ec4e1fbd47725cf","tid":1936624,"uid":12404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"男仔同男同學扑嘢好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"你點知係男同學架！！！<br />\n<br />\n案103為案59(高中生)之<span style=\"color: red;\">同班男同學</span>，與案59座位鄰近，3月15日早上出現喉嚨癢，當晚有發燒症狀，16日先行致電1922通知後，依指示前往醫院就醫並主動告知為案59同學，隨即由醫院安排採檢後住院隔離，於今日確診。因應該班級已有2人確診，該校自3月20日至3月27日進行全校停課。"},{"pid":"9d65bd9aa4c64a1fd742baf696908d7b9e29a1e4","tid":1936624,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"性交會傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e0e0094d5f4ad024e8f3993a214da10e68fb09","tid":1936624,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"唔同老豆老母一齊同檯食飯囉。"},{"pid":"9f159205b74acdcb7169cbcb24f2af08735497e8","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0d02a79f7254c40185f7071985c27506b749034","tid":1936624,"uid":11301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"學生間的互動更親密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"案130為案59<span style=\"color: red;\">同班女同學</span>，3月17日發病，經採檢通報於今日確診，為該班級第3名確診個案；3人就讀學校已自今日起停課至3月27日。"},{"pid":"8d4ec8acf3b47c0633b67155032742a99555c899","tid":1936624,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"與兩位同學進行親密接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55a17e9348bf9e96a1069d73702bc165856857b","tid":1936624,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"兩男一女可以做啲咩接觸呢？"},{"pid":"3db45ef625eddd377e7fb3de9832c419fa31958a","tid":1936624,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d4ec8acf3b47c0633b67155032742a99555c899","tid":1936624,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"與兩位同學進行親密接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"濃厚接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{